Wait, let me look at the other fountains and boulders. Okay, there are some fountains: (38, 12), (38, 14), (39, 14). There are boulders at (36, 13) and (38, 13).

Okay, let's go back. The current boulder is at (41, 10). It was *originally* at (40, 10). No, wait... it was at (39, 10) because ` was at (39,10)? But { was at (40, 10), so I am mixing up the symbols.
