I've located the boulders at (35,13), (38,12), (41,10) and (42,14), and fountains at (40,10) and (38,14) and (39,14).  It seems that I've been misreading where some of the characters are located. Initially, I thought I'd get to (38,13) and try to push the boulder north, but there's a wall.  So, I re-checked and corrected by understanding of all of the characters in the game. I see a boulder at 8,10, which looks accessible from (9,10).

